570
00:29:52,270 --> 00:29:53,960
what should I say?

571
00:29:55,830 --> 00:29:56,760
Tell him exactly

572
00:29:57,920 --> 00:29:59,120
what you just told me.

573
00:30:00,720 --> 00:30:01,350
Yibo,

574
00:30:02,590 --> 00:30:03,590
telling the truth

575
00:30:04,050 --> 00:30:05,910
is always more useful than lying.

576
00:30:11,070 --> 00:30:11,680
Okay.

577
00:30:17,270 --> 00:30:18,000
Chief Zhang.

578
00:30:18,160 --> 00:30:19,550
I've thought it through.

579
00:30:19,550 --> 00:30:21,160
Please come to Fenglinwan again.

580
00:30:21,160 --> 00:30:22,620
I'll tell you everything.

581
00:30:22,880 --> 00:30:23,350
Okay.

582
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:25,280
Very good.

583
00:30:25,830 --> 00:30:26,360
Goodbye.

584
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:28,940
Chief,

585
00:30:29,160 --> 00:30:30,030
working cases with you

586
00:30:30,030 --> 00:30:31,840
feels easier than ever.

587
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:35,700
Why do I feel like something is fishy?

588
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:37,610
Could this be a trap?

589
00:30:38,110 --> 00:30:39,040
What do you mean?

590
00:30:39,680 --> 00:30:40,540
Think about it.

591
00:30:40,680 --> 00:30:42,290
Lu Yibo wrote the report letter

592
00:30:42,290 --> 00:30:44,420
and sent it to the provincial capital—

593
00:30:44,590 --> 00:30:45,920
which means

594
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:47,850
he originally intended to report.

595
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:49,720
But then he took

596
00:30:50,270 --> 00:30:51,600
the report letter back—

597
00:30:51,960 --> 00:30:53,750
which means he didn't want to report.

598
00:30:53,750 --> 00:30:54,880
When we tracked him down,

599
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:56,200
he admitted it immediately—

600
00:30:56,200 --> 00:30:57,790
which means he did want to report.

601
00:30:57,790 --> 00:30:58,880
But he hesitated and wouldn'ts say

602
00:30:58,880 --> 00:31:00,080
who he was reporting—

603
00:31:00,550 --> 00:31:02,610
which means he didn't want to report.

604
00:31:03,480 --> 00:31:05,210
Now he's asking us to come over—

605
00:31:05,440 --> 00:31:07,400
which means he wants to report again.

606
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:09,000
Does he want to report or not?

607
00:31:10,150 --> 00:31:12,750
This guy's living
in constant contradiction.

608
00:31:14,310 --> 00:31:16,260
Could it be that he's terrified

609
00:31:16,310 --> 00:31:17,480
of the person he's reporting,

610
00:31:17,480 --> 00:31:19,010
so he's deeply conflicted?

611
00:31:20,070 --> 00:31:21,400
If he were truly terrified,

612
00:31:21,400 --> 00:31:22,640
he wouldn't have used his real name.

613
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:23,640
But he didn't report under his real name.

614
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:24,830
There was no name on that report letter.

615
00:31:24,830 --> 00:31:27,230
It was only because Chief Zhang stepped...

616
00:31:30,640 --> 00:31:32,590
Chief Zhang stepped on a piece of paper,

617
00:31:32,590 --> 00:31:34,390
then we found the report letter.

618
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:36,640
So,

619
00:31:37,750 --> 00:31:38,790
I'm wondering

620
00:31:39,400 --> 00:31:40,270
whether all of this

621
00:31:40,270 --> 00:31:41,680
is a big misleading.

622
00:31:42,510 --> 00:31:44,170
It feels more like a trap to me.

623
00:31:47,590 --> 00:31:49,320
Chief Zhang, what do you think?

624
00:32:06,880 --> 00:32:07,550
The night

625
00:32:08,550 --> 00:32:10,200
gave me dark eyes,

626
00:32:12,350 --> 00:32:15,240
but I use them to seek the light.

627
00:32:20,530 --> 00:32:24,660
[Fenglinwan]

628
00:32:52,550 --> 00:32:53,200
Chief Zhang,

629
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:55,260
how should we question him this time?

630
00:32:56,550 --> 00:32:57,750
If you're planning to improvise again,

631
00:32:57,750 --> 00:32:59,000
give me a heads-up first.

632
00:32:59,000 --> 00:33:00,510
I'm worried I won’t catch the setup

633
00:33:00,510 --> 00:33:01,350
and drop the whole act.

634
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:01,830
No.

635
00:33:03,270 --> 00:33:04,270
Let's do it like last time.

636
00:33:04,270 --> 00:33:05,030
Didn't that work pretty well?

637
00:33:05,030 --> 00:33:06,430
We'll just play it by ear.

638
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:08,150
It seems

639
00:33:08,240 --> 00:33:10,170
we can only fill in the gaps as we go.

640
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:13,810
What kind of jargon are you talking about?

641
00:33:15,310 --> 00:33:17,170
You don't watch crosstalk at all?

642
00:33:21,440 --> 00:33:22,220
Let's say,

643
00:33:22,350 --> 00:33:23,400
spend 200 yuan

644
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:24,830
to buy a little golden piggy.

645
00:33:24,830 --> 00:33:26,160
It squeals when it drinks water,

646
00:33:26,160 --> 00:33:27,640
crunches when it eats beans.

647
00:33:27,640 --> 00:33:28,630
Along the wall,

648
00:33:28,680 --> 00:33:30,110
then toss it outside.

649
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:31,270
And it gives a squeak.

650
00:33:31,270 --> 00:33:32,390
Guess what?

651
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:34,840
It's dead?

652
00:33:37,310 --> 00:33:38,240
Is it dead ot not?

653
00:33:49,510 --> 00:33:50,310
Have some tea.

654
00:33:58,480 --> 00:34:00,010
I've figured it out myself.

655
00:34:00,400 --> 00:34:01,210
Actually,

656
00:34:01,270 --> 00:34:02,750
about the report letter earlier,

657
00:34:02,750 --> 00:34:04,880
I felt I owed you a proper explanation.

658
00:34:08,110 --> 00:34:09,000
We can drink this tea now, right?

659
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:10,130
Yes, yes, of course.

660
00:34:15,230 --> 00:34:15,710
Well,

661
00:34:17,400 --> 00:34:18,170
Mr. Lu

662
00:34:18,320 --> 00:34:19,190
is Sanjiangkou's

663
00:34:19,190 --> 00:34:20,590
outstanding entrepreneur.

664
00:34:20,590 --> 00:34:21,150
I'm flattered.

665
00:34:21,150 --> 00:34:21,790
And we

666
00:34:21,840 --> 00:34:23,900
are also willing to hear your report.

667
00:34:29,670 --> 00:34:30,860
But actually, that report letter

668
00:34:30,860 --> 00:34:31,460
is fake.

669
00:34:34,480 --> 00:34:35,230
Fake?

670
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:38,540
Mr. Lu,

671
00:34:38,840 --> 00:34:41,030
writing a false report letter
is against the law.

672
00:34:41,030 --> 00:34:41,409
Yes.

673
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:42,320
That's exactly why I rushed

674
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:43,440
to the provincial capital
overnight to retrieve it.

675
00:34:43,440 --> 00:34:44,000
I didn't expect

676
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:45,800
it'd cause such a big misunderstanding.

677
00:34:45,800 --> 00:34:47,190
It really took up

678
00:34:47,230 --> 00:34:48,510
our valuable police resources.

679
00:34:48,510 --> 00:34:51,239
I'm willing to accept
any punishment or penalty.

680
00:35:01,070 --> 00:35:01,880
The provincial capital explosion case—

681
00:35:01,880 --> 00:35:03,880
does it have anything to do with you?

682
00:35:05,480 --> 00:35:07,610
You mean the manhole cover explosion?

683
00:35:07,630 --> 00:35:08,360
That has absolutely

684
00:35:08,360 --> 00:35:09,560
nothing to do with me.

685
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:10,960
Then what a coincidence

686
00:35:10,960 --> 00:35:11,590
that you just happened to be there

687
00:35:11,590 --> 00:35:12,840
at the explosion site.

688
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:13,900
What a coincidence indeed.

689
00:35:13,900 --> 00:35:14,670
But the explosion

690
00:35:14,670 --> 00:35:16,230
has absolutely nothing to do with me.

691
00:35:16,230 --> 00:35:17,630
I was a victim too.

692
00:35:17,760 --> 00:35:18,960
I got covered in shit.

693
00:35:20,480 --> 00:35:21,440
What kind of terrorist

694
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:23,100
gets himself covered in shit?

695
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:24,600
Wait a minute.

696
00:35:31,150 --> 00:35:32,080
Liu'an Guapian.

697
00:35:32,240 --> 00:35:33,050
Good tea.

698
00:35:33,110 --> 00:35:34,310
It is Liu'an Guapian.

699
00:35:34,670 --> 00:35:35,200
Officer,

700
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:37,400
you pronounced "Guapian" right.

701
00:35:37,400 --> 00:35:38,280
But the first two characters,

702
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:38,880
Lu'an.

703
00:35:40,070 --> 00:35:40,730
It's Lu'an.

704
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:43,360
Yeah.

705
00:35:43,490 --> 00:35:44,000
Right.

706
00:35:44,230 --> 00:35:44,670
Lu'an.

707
00:35:45,400 --> 00:35:46,000
Look at me—

708
00:35:46,960 --> 00:35:48,230
my taste buds got it right,

709
00:35:48,230 --> 00:35:49,510
but my mouth slipped
and said the wrong thing.

710
00:35:49,510 --> 00:35:50,640
It's Lu'an Guapian.

711
00:35:51,880 --> 00:35:52,440
Nice tea.

712
00:36:00,510 --> 00:36:01,710
You...

713
00:36:02,370 --> 00:36:03,360
What... what Liu?

714
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:04,220
Lu'an Guapian.

715
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:05,140
Lu'an Guapian.

716
00:36:05,670 --> 00:36:06,530
Let me try some.

717
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:11,920
Mr. Lu.

718
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:13,840
Didn't you understand

719
00:36:13,840 --> 00:36:15,170
what Chief Zhang meant?

720
00:36:15,230 --> 00:36:16,960
There was a hidden message in his words.

721
00:36:16,960 --> 00:36:19,150
Right now, we're simply asking questions.

722
00:36:19,150 --> 00:36:20,230
But if this turns into an interrogation,

723
00:36:20,230 --> 00:36:22,150
it would be a very different conversation.

724
00:36:22,150 --> 00:36:23,510
Understood. Understood.

725
00:36:23,510 --> 00:36:25,840
Chief Zhang truly is a great detective
from the Provincial Department.

726
00:36:25,840 --> 00:36:27,840
Nothing can possibly hide from him.

727
00:36:28,150 --> 00:36:29,150
He's reminding me

728
00:36:29,150 --> 00:36:30,280
to watch what I say.

729
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:33,570
You're very sharp.

730
00:36:33,760 --> 00:36:34,560
In that case,

731
00:36:34,590 --> 00:36:35,790
let's keep it simple.

732
00:36:35,800 --> 00:36:37,960
Let's put everything on the table.

733
00:36:44,880 --> 00:36:45,540
Is there...

734
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:49,720
an unspoken reason behind this?

735
00:36:55,450 --> 00:36:57,440
I'm not capable!

736
00:37:00,190 --> 00:37:01,850
You figured that out already?

737
00:37:02,800 --> 00:37:03,280
Well,

738
00:37:03,640 --> 00:37:04,590
it's obvious.

739
00:37:04,630 --> 00:37:05,360
Too obvious.

740
00:37:05,920 --> 00:37:07,320
How could I not notice it?

741
00:37:08,030 --> 00:37:08,800
Just tell us.

742
00:37:09,110 --> 00:37:10,440
We will keep it a secret.

743
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:12,110
The unspoken reason...

744
00:37:12,110 --> 00:37:13,510
is my private matter.

745
00:37:14,550 --> 00:37:15,880
But regarding that report letter,

746
00:37:15,880 --> 00:37:17,210
it's authentically...

747
00:37:17,230 --> 00:37:18,150
fake.

748
00:37:19,280 --> 00:37:20,250
Is it true or false?

749
00:37:20,250 --> 00:37:21,150
Don't leave us hanging,

750
00:37:21,150 --> 00:37:21,710
okay?

751
00:37:22,320 --> 00:37:24,920
I told you this guy is
a walking contradiction.

752
00:37:25,190 --> 00:37:26,710
Whether it's true or false,

753
00:37:26,710 --> 00:37:28,310
you wrote the report letter,

754
00:37:28,550 --> 00:37:30,280
so we still have to look into it.

755
00:37:36,230 --> 00:37:37,090
We already know

756
00:37:37,110 --> 00:37:38,370
that you reported him.

757
00:37:39,510 --> 00:37:41,150
The question is, why did you...

758
00:37:41,150 --> 00:37:42,770
I did report him.

759
00:37:42,960 --> 00:37:43,510
But everything I wrote

760
00:37:43,510 --> 00:37:44,670
was all made up.

761
00:37:44,800 --> 00:37:46,460
So it doesn't matter who it is.

762
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:48,280
Since it doesn't matter,

763
00:37:48,710 --> 00:37:49,920
then why are you hiding it?

764
00:37:49,920 --> 00:37:50,400
Right.

765
00:37:50,960 --> 00:37:52,630
Let's just be straight with each other.

766
00:37:52,630 --> 00:37:53,830
Let's talk about him.

767
00:37:56,000 --> 00:37:56,840
I reported Zhou Rong,

768
00:37:56,840 --> 00:37:58,770
but it was a big misunderstanding.

769
00:38:10,670 --> 00:38:12,330
You and Zhou Rong are friends.

770
00:38:14,150 --> 00:38:15,750
More than friends, I assume?

771
00:38:16,540 --> 00:38:17,920
We're close friends. Childhood friends.

772
00:38:17,920 --> 00:38:19,630
Since you are childhood friends,

773
00:38:19,630 --> 00:38:20,840
whether it's true or false,

774
00:38:20,840 --> 00:38:22,500
this just doesn't make sense.

775
00:38:26,070 --> 00:38:27,480
Why did you report Zhou Rong?
